    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not-assessed at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 requirements for Class II CPB devices. Discretization error exceeds requirement (achieved 3 vs. required 2), providing additional confidence in mesh-independent hemolysis predictions. Output comparison demonstrates NIH predictions within 25% acceptance band across all 5 operating points. RH < 1 confirmed for COU operating range. Package is submitted under ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending completion of institutional signature workflow and will be appended prior to regulatory submission.",
